parameters.name: EndTime
parameters.description: The end of the time range to query. Specify the time in the `yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mmZ` format. The time must be in UTC.

parameters.name: Key
parameters.description: The performance metrics that you want to query. Separate multiple indicators with commas (,). For more information, see [Performance parameters](~~141787~~).

parameters.name: StartTime
parameters.description: The beginning of the time range to query. Specify the time in the `yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mmZ` format. The time must be in UTC.
